Privacy Policy

Last updated: 8/15/2025

Budgetix respects your privacy rights.
We do not collect, store, or share any personal information except as described in this policy.

1. Information Collection and Use

The app does not collect or transmit personal data to any external servers.
All data you enter (expenses, income, and other information) is stored locally on your device.

2. Data Access and Sharing

The app does not share your data with third parties.
We do not use advertising networks or analytics services that collect user information.

3. Permissions

The app may request access to your device storage solely to save and restore your local data.
This data never leaves your device.

4. Security

We take reasonable measures to protect your information.
However, we recommend that you regularly back up your data to avoid accidental loss.

5. Changes to This Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time.
Any changes will be posted in this document.

6. Contact Us

If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:
